      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="faq">
        <strong>What are your hygiene practices?</strong>
        <p>All tools are autoclave sterilized. Foot baths are disinfected after each use. Our techs wear gloves when required.</p>
        <strong>Do you offer treatments and add-ons?</strong>
        <p>Yes, including hot stones, scrubs, masks, and strengthening treatments for brittle nails.</p>
        <strong>Can I choose my nail technician?</strong>
        <p>Absolutely! Meet our team above or request a preferred specialist when booking.</p>
        <strong>What products do you use?</strong>
        <p>We feature OPI, CND, and cruelty-free vegan polish brands. Hypoallergenic options available.</p>
        <strong>How long do services take?</strong>
        <p>Manicure (30‚Äì45 min), Pedicure (45‚Äì60 min), Gel or Acrylics (60‚Äì90 min). Combo services available.</p>
        <strong>What are your maintenance recommendations?</strong>
        <p>Moisturize cuticles, use gloves for chores, and avoid harsh soaps. Gel nails last 2‚Äì3 weeks, classic ~1 week.</p>
        <strong>Do you offer gel, dip, and acrylic?</strong>
        <p>Yes! We explain pros/cons and help you transition between types if desired.</p>
        <strong>Can you help with nail health?</strong>
        <p>Yes. We offer growth-strengthening treatments and educate clients on aftercare and healthy habits.</p>
        <strong>Any home care product suggestions?</strong>
